<L>__{exterior small rural village. main street. day.}
<A>__{a three store town. a couple of pickup trucks parked in front of the country store. scott's mustang parked next to them. a large, filled, double length log truck speeds through the village. scott, in his lumber jacket, is assembling various maintenance items on the checkout counter. a large paintbrush, several boxes of nails, a gallon of painterior the proprietor, a good natured fellow in his fifties, comes up to the counter to check scott out.}
